# EXCLUDE EVERYTHING by default
*

# Whitelist only the files we want public
!docs/
!docs/**
!README.md
!.gitignore

# Never commit, even if accidentally added
**/lists/
**/*.csv
**/*.xlsx
**/*.docx
**/*-pnl.html
**/*-list.html
**/workout-*
**/cape-town-*
**/artist-statement-*
**/trackstack_api_*
**/setup_trackstack_*
**/yaffa_custom_audience*
**/yaffa_customer_match*
.DS_Store
*.env
*.env.*
.credentials/
yaffa-ops-export-*.json
